org.perfcake.reporting.destination

Class CrystalDestination

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.reporting.destination.AbstractDestination
      • org.perfcake.reporting.destination.CrystalDestination
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, Destination

    public class CrystalDestination
extends AbstractDestination
    A destination that performs heuristics for anomalies detection and compiles all tests results into one document report.
    Author:
    Martina Kůrová
